Liz Larsen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liz_Larsen 0 Liz Larsen (born January 16, 1959 in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania) is an American actress. She is best known for playing Jessica Reed on Law Order. Larsen received a Tony Award nomination for The Most Happy Fella revival (1992) and has also appeared on Broadway in Hairspray, The Rocky Horror Show, Damn Yankees, Starmites, and Fiddler on the Roof. She has performed in Beautiful: The Carole King Musical since its opening in 2014. Larsen attended New Hope Solebury High School in New Hope, Bucks County PA.
